window.bookSummaryJSON = "The first novel of J. R. Ward's <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Black Dagger Brotherhood series features a unique take on vampire lore and heavy doses of sensuality. <p>The vampire Darius fears for the life of his half-breed daughter, who is unaware of her unusual destiny. To oversee her transformation, Darius seeks help from Wrath, a dangerous loner and the world's only purebred vampire.</p>"; 
